        <item>
            <title>【評測】CCSToys 真三一斬星斧版　新設計頭部 + 斬星斧夠霸氣</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/27/ccstoysgetter/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ccstoysgetter</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/04/27/ccstoysgetter/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Gary Lee]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 03:00:45 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[玩具]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Figure]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[超合金]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[高達]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1231518</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>CCSToys 的出品一向也保持高質，但今次的真三一同一模具但出第三次的版本，真三一斬星斧版 (Getter One Stars Slasher Ver)，(前兩次是初版及限定黑版)，今次的版本又表現如何呢？</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231760" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc8993-694x499.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="499" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc8993-694x499.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc8993.jpg 1251w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲包裝盒明顯比舊版扇了，但也是很大盒</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231761" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc8999-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc8999-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc8999.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲真三一斬星斧版的彩繪</p><h2>開箱：燈效及底座確定保留</h2><p>其實今次的真三一斬星斧版是提早推出了，之前本身是預計 5 月才推出的，之前預告推出時，見到售價下調了，見到網上有玩家提出疑問，除了武器量減少外，會否連燈效及底座都會被削減了？小編收到後當然立即開箱看看這兩方面，可以確定燈效及底座都有保留到，玩家們不用擔心。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231762" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9001-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9001-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9001.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231763" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9003-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9003-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9003.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲是有底座的，不用擔心</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231764" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9005-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9005-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9005.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲燈效全也保留的</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231765" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9007-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9007-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9007.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲三對造型手掌，及一對可動手掌</p><h2>斬星斧版改進地方</h2><p>今次最大特色就是其金屬紅色的配色，所有裝甲部位都改用有光澤的塗裝，更配合到真三一的感覺，更長更有型的新翼，不僅在大小和造型上有所增強，其可動性和可玩性也得到了提升，這一改進讓飛翼能夠模擬動畫中的高速飛行模式。新頭部的造型更有動畫設定感，眼珠更大更精靈了，線條也改了，以及加入更多透明綠色部份，胸甲部份的藍色位置也改為透明綠色，內部則以銀色製作，就算不著燈時，層次及機械感覺更加強烈，當然著燈後的燈效也更為突出。可説整隻新版外觀，絕對比舊版更加有型靚仔。</p><p><a title="_DSC9046" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53681456693/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53681456693_8d0ba46070_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9046" width="657" height="1024" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲金屬紅色的配色，所有裝甲部位都改用有光澤的塗裝</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231769" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9050-1-643x580.jpg" alt="" width="643" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9050-1-643x580.jpg 643w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9050-1.jpg 997w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 643px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲更長更有型的新翼</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231770" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9024-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9024-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9024.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231771" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9025-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9025-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9025.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲新頭部的造型更有動畫設定感，眼珠更大更精靈了</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231772" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9026-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9026-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9026.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲胸甲部份的藍色位置也改為透明綠色，內部則以銀色製作</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231773" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9027-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9027-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9027.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231774" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9039-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9039-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9039.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲就算不著燈時，層次及機械感覺更加強烈</p><p><a title="_DSC9193" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53681687520/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53681687520_ed4ea391b7_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9193" width="749" height="1024" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲著燈後的燈效也更為突出</p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231775" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9017-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9017-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9017.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231778" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9194-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9194-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9194.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231780" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9196-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9196-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9196.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231781" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9197-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9197-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9197.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><a title="_DSC9096" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53680369872/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53680369872_7a4d55e0db_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9096" width="1024" height="721" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可模擬動畫中的高速飛行模式</p><p>雖然真三一斬星斧版在武器方面只提供一把特製的大斧，與初版和黑色版的多樣武器相比略顯單薄。然而，這把斬星斧可以改變刀刃的擺放方式，亦可以變換成鐮刀狀，全展開時非常大把亦很夠霸氣。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231783" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9054-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9054-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9054.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231788" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9059-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9059-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9059.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲新的斬星斧非常巨大</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231784" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9055-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9055-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9055.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲可拉開作鐮刀狀態</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231785" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9056-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9056-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9056.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231786" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9057-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9057-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9057.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲不同的掌型都是為配合斬星斧握法而設</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231787" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9058-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9058-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9058.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1231789" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9062-567x580.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9062-567x580.jpg 567w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/dsc9062.jpg 880w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 567px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲附設的地台</p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/22/bandai-g-frame/life-tech/%e7%8e%a9%e5%85%b7/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Bandai 食玩樂園登陸葵芳     G-FRAME FA 風靈彩透 + MJ GUNDAM SP 版</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/03/05/gundam-factory-yokohama-5/hottopic/walk/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">橫濱可動高達 3 月底結束展出，閉幕禮富野由悠季 + 無人機 + 煙花</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><h2>Action Pose</h2><p><a title="_DSC9069" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53681595319/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53681595319_c017523133_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9069" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC9074" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53680369947/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53680369947_b82a261b51_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9074" width="1024" height="595" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC9078" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53681227691/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53681227691_66a9fc5567_b.jpg" alt="_DSC9078" width="1024" height="576" /></a><script async src="//embedr.flickr.com/assets/client-code.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p><a title="_DSC9093" href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/100967552@N06/53680369942/in/dateposted-public/" data-flickr-embed="true"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter" src="https://live.staticflickr.com/65535/53680369942_558ba60631_b.j